726885f-a.title: Queens: Hollis Avenue - 102nd Street
726885f-a.text:
Hollis Ave. (foreground), at the S.W. corner of 102nd Street,
showing in a set of two views the David Purdy house thereon. 0ther
owners were C. Mott, 1860; D. J. Purdy, 1873-1891; amd two sisters
and a brother of David S. Purdy in 1934.
May 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.

726880f-a.title: Queens: Hollis Avenue - 102nd Avenue
726880f-a.text:
Hollis Ave., east side, opposite 1O2nd Ave., showing fully
the A. Oakley Eetcham house. D. Eetcham and E. Mason were the
owners in 1891 and 1896 respectively.
May 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
